OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777727463
OL,3,CNorthern Irish TV star Gloria
OL,4,CHunniford to receive Freedom of the
OL,5,CCity of London
OL,7,FTV presenter Gloria Hunniford is to
OL,8,Freceive The Freedom of the City of
OL,9,FLondon at an event in the city's
OL,10,Fhistoric Guildhall.
OL,12,FThe Northern Irish star, who is best
OL,13,Fknown for her work on shows such as
OL,14,FRip Off Britain, Loose Women and The
OL,15,FOne Show, will receive the honour on
OL,16,FMay 14.
OL,18,FShe said: "This will be an extremely
OL,19,Fspecial and exciting day for me and my
OL,20,Ffamily and I am delighted that I have
OL,21,Fbeen chosen to receive this honour.
OL,26,@zD@KOU
