PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777727463
OL,3,CNorthern Irish TV star Gloria
OL,4,CHunniford to receive Freedom of the
OL,5,CCity of London
OL,7,F"Since being given a job at BBC Radio
OL,8,F2 in the 80s, London has been my home
OL,9,Fand some of my most treasured moments
OL,10,Fin broadcasting have taken place in
OL,11,Fthis city, so it is extremely humbling
OL,12,Fthat I have been awarded this
OL,13,Faccolade."
OL,15,FIn 2017, Hunniford became an OBE in
OL,16,Fthe Queen's Birthday Honours for her
OL,17,Fcontribution to cancer charities
OL,18,Fthrough breast screening services and
OL,19,Fcancer support.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]
