OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777727463
OL,3,CNorthern Irish TV star Gloria
OL,4,CHunniford to receive Freedom of the
OL,5,CCity of London
OL,7,FShe was also awarded the freedom of
OL,8,Fher County Armagh home borough in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland in 2024, becoming the
OL,10,Ffirst woman to receive the honour for
OL,11,Fher outstanding contributions to
OL,12,Fbroadcasting and charity.
OL,14,FAfter receiving the honour, she said:
OL,15,F"County Armagh and Portadown, my home
OL,16,Ftown, has always held a very special
OL,17,Fplace in my heart, and to be
OL,18,Frecognised in this way is incredibly
OL,19,Fhumbling ` it's great to be home."
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@bO]
