OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1777727463
OL,3,CNorthern Irish TV star Gloria
OL,4,CHunniford to receive Freedom of the
OL,5,CCity of London
OL,7,FThe presenter set up the Caron Keating
OL,8,FFoundation in memory of her daughter,
OL,9,Fwho died from breast cancer in 2004.
OL,11,FHunniford is also known for her
OL,12,Fappearance on the BBC's Strictly Come
OL,13,FDancing in 2005, where she was
OL,14,Fpartnered by professional dancer
OL,15,FDarren Bennett and eliminated in the
OL,16,Fthird week during the show's third
OL,17,Fseries.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
