OL,3,CNorthern Irish TV star Gloria
OL,4,CHunniford to receive Freedom of the
OL,5,CCity of London
OL,7,FShe lost her husband of more than 20
OL,8,Fyears, Stephen Way, in 2024 and said
OL,9,Fhe had left "the most enormous void,
OL,10,Fnot only in my life".
OL,12,FLast year, she took part in The Great
OL,13,FCelebrity Bake Off For Stand Up To
OL,14,FCancer.
